getResult

public org.bukkit.event.Event.Result getResult()
Get's the result of this event. Default: Allow for Minecraft to handle the inventory click normally Allow: Allow the inventory click to continue, regardless of the consequences Deny: Block the inventory click from occuring, reset the inventory state to the pre-click state

Returns:
result
